          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>No Windfalls for Government Service Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to establish a $1 million lifetime limitation on the nonrecognition of a taxpayer's gains from the sale of property pursuant to a certificate of divesture to comply with conflict-of-interest requirements for certain federal government positions. </p>]]></text>
